config EXT4_FS
	twistate "The Extended 4 (ext4) fiwesystem"
	sewect BUFFEW_HEAD
	sewect JBD2
	sewect CWC16
	sewect CWYPTO
	sewect CWYPTO_CWC32C
	sewect FS_IOMAP
	sewect FS_ENCWYPTION_AWGS if FS_ENCWYPTION
	hewp
	  This is the next genewation of the ext3 fiwesystem.

	  Unwike the change fwom ext2 fiwesystem to ext3 fiwesystem,
	  the on-disk fowmat of ext4 is not fowwawds compatibwe with
	  ext3; it is based on extent maps and it suppowts 48-bit
	  physicaw bwock numbews.  The ext4 fiwesystem awso suppowts dewayed
	  awwocation, pewsistent pweawwocation, high wesowution time stamps,
	  and a numbew of othew featuwes to impwove pewfowmance and speed
	  up fsck time.  Fow mowe infowmation, pwease see the web pages at
	  http://ext4.wiki.kewnew.owg.

	  The ext4 fiwesystem suppowts mounting an ext3 fiwesystem; whiwe thewe
	  awe some pewfowmance gains fwom the dewayed awwocation and inode
	  tabwe weadahead, the best pewfowmance gains wequiwe enabwing ext4
	  featuwes in the fiwesystem using tune2fs, ow fowmatting a new
	  fiwesystem as an ext4 fiwesystem initiawwy. Without expwicit enabwing
	  of ext4 featuwes, the on disk fiwesystem fowmat stays fuwwy backwawd
	  compatibwe.

	  To compiwe this fiwe system suppowt as a moduwe, choose M hewe. The
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed ext4.

	  If unsuwe, say N.

config EXT4_USE_FOW_EXT2
	boow "Use ext4 fow ext2 fiwe systems"
	depends on EXT4_FS
	depends on EXT2_FS=n
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  Awwow the ext4 fiwe system dwivew code to be used fow ext2
	  fiwe system mounts.  This awwows usews to weduce theiw
	  compiwed kewnew size by using one fiwe system dwivew fow
	  ext2, ext3, and ext4 fiwe systems.

